    Frequently Asked Questions

    Are Chinology™ masks compatible
    with all skin types?

    The medical silicone automatically adapts to your skin hence Chinology™ masks are compatible for all women and skin types.

    If you want to get the best results, we recommend applying it twice a week to get even more visible results!

    How many times can I reuse a Chinology™ mask?

    Each Chinology™ mask is designed for up to 10 uses, making it a smart and economical choice.


    Instead of single-use products, you can enjoy the benefits of the mask over multiple sessions.


    Simply follow the care instructions, and your mask will stay effective every time!

    How do Chinology™ masks work?

    When the Chinology™ mask is applied to the skin, the medical silicone creates a micro-climate between the mask and your skin.

    Two benefits occur:

    - The cells are regenerated: The regenerating cells of the lower layers of the skin are attracted to the upper layers.

    - Blood flow increases: the compression of the mask increases blood flow to purify the skin and restore its vitality.

    The medical silicone acts at the heart of the cells to guarantee an instant and lasting result.

    Is Chinology™ Mask pricey?

    “£29.95 a piece seems too high for a face mask. Is Chinology™ pricey?”


    Absolutely not! Because each Chinology™ mask is reusable up to 10 times over.


    While our 50% sale lasts, it’s currently priced at just £29.95, bringing the price of a single session down to a mere £4.99, which is more affordable than most regular face masks.


    And if you bundle up and purchase two packs, you can save as much as 70%!


    This makes Chinology a more economic and much safer option to get rid of double chin than surgery or Kybella injections, which usually start above £2,000 per session, with multiple sessions required for lasting results.


    How long do you have to use them
    to get visible results?

    Simply use the Chinology™ masks once a week for 5-10 minutes on the areas to be treated.

    The results appear from the first session to have a smoother skin and eliminate remove the double chin easily and quickly!

    Are Chinology™ masks safe to wear?

    Yes, unlike skin creams and face lifts that can damage your skin and have the opposite effect in the long run, Chinology™ masks are environmentally friendly and safe for your health

    Thanks to the medical silicone, your double chin will disappear in a totally natural way and will allow you to save money on skin creams.
